# Sustainability DX Toolkit: ML for EDGE Zero Carbon ROI

**Author**: James Amoah, CEO Jakag Engineering | IFC EDGE Expert | UT McCombs AI/ML 2027

### Business Problem
Japan construction must cut 46% CO2 by 2030. Which 1,000 buildings should Takenaka retrofit first for max ROI?

### Solution: DX for Sustainability  
This repo uses Python + GCP + IFC EDGE standards to model energy, water, materials savings. Input: building data. Output: CO2 tons saved + ¥ payback period.

### Tech Stack
Python, Pandas, Scikit-learn, Vertex AI, BigQuery, IFC EDGE API

### Status
Capstone project for UT McCombs PGP-AIML. Live Feb 2027. Used by Jakag Engineering for client proposals in Ghana.

